#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Google Cloud Functions (Serverless) with Quarkus REST, Undertow, or Reactive Routes"
msgstr "结合 Quarkus REST、Undertow 或 Reactive Routes 的 Google Cloud Functions（无服务器）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"This extension's backward compatibility and presence in the ecosystem is not guaranteed\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">preview</a>"
msgstr "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"无法保证此扩展程序的向后兼容性及其在生态系统中的可用性\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">预览</a>"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `quarkus-google-cloud-functions-http` extension allows you to write microservices with Quarkus REST (Jakarta REST),\n"
"Undertow (Servlet), Reactive Routes, or xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP], and make these microservices deployable to the Google Cloud Functions runtime."
msgstr "`quarkus-google-cloud-functions-http` 扩展允许您使用 Quarkus REST（Jakarta REST）、Undertow（Servlet）、Reactive Routes 或 xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] 编写微服务，并将这些微服务部署到 Google Cloud Functions 运行时环境中。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "One Google Cloud Functions deployment can represent any number of Jakarta REST, Servlet, Reactive Routes, or xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] endpoints."
msgstr "一个 Google Cloud Functions 部署可以代表任意数量的 Jakarta REST、Servlet、Reactive Routes 或 xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] 端点。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "先决条件"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://cloud.google.com/[A Google Cloud Account]. Free accounts work."
msgstr "link:https://cloud.google.com/[一个 Google Cloud 账户] 。免费账户即可。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://cloud.google.com/sdk[Cloud SDK CLI Installed]"
msgstr "link:https://cloud.google.com/sdk[已安装 Cloud SDK CLI]"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Solution"
msgstr "解决方案"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This guide walks you through generating a sample project followed by creating three HTTP endpoints\n"
"written with Jakarta REST APIs, Servlet APIs, Reactive Routes, or xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] APIs. Once built, you will be able to deploy\n"
"the project to Google Cloud."
msgstr "本指南将引导您生成一个示例项目，随后使用 Jakarta REST API、Servlet API、Reactive Routes 或 xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] API 创建三个 HTTP 端点。构建完成后，您将能够将该项目部署到 Google Cloud。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you don't want to follow all these steps, you can go right to the completed example."
msgstr "如果您不想按照所有这些步骤操作，可以直接查看已完成的示例。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Clone the Git repository: `git clone {quickstarts-clone-url}`, or download an {quickstarts-archive-url}[archive]."
msgstr "克隆 Git 仓库： `git clone {quickstarts-clone-url}` ，或下载 {quickstarts-archive-url}[存档]。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The solution is located in the `google-cloud-functions-http-quickstart` link:{quickstarts-tree-url}/google-cloud-functions-http-quickstart[directory]."
msgstr "该解决方案位于 `google-cloud-functions-http-quickstart` link:{quickstarts-tree-url}/google-cloud-functions-http-quickstart[目录] 中。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Creating the Maven Deployment Project"
msgstr "创建 Maven 部署项目"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Create an application with the `quarkus-google-cloud-functions-http` extension.\n"
"You can use the following Maven command to create it:"
msgstr "使用 `quarkus-google-cloud-functions-http` 扩展创建一个应用程序。您可以使用以下 Maven 命令进行创建："

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Login to Google Cloud"
msgstr "登录 Google Cloud"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Login to Google Cloud is necessary for deploying the application. It can be done as follows:"
msgstr "部署应用程序需要登录 Google Cloud。具体操作如下："

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Creating the endpoints"
msgstr "创建端点"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For this example project, we will create four endpoints, one for Quarkus REST (Jakarta REST), one for Undertow (Servlet),\n"
"one for Reactive routes and one for xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP]."
msgstr "在这个示例项目中，我们将创建四个端点：一个用于 Quarkus REST（Jakarta REST），一个用于 Undertow（Servlet），一个用于 Reactive 路由，还有一个用于 xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"These various endpoints are for demonstration purposes.\n"
"For real life applications, you should choose one of these technologies and stick to it."
msgstr "这些不同的端点仅用于演示目的。在实际应用中，您应选择其中一种技术并坚持使用。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you don't need endpoints of each type, you can remove the corresponding extensions from your `pom.xml`."
msgstr "如果您不需要每种类型的端点，可以从 `pom.xml` 中删除相应的扩展。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Jakarta REST endpoint"
msgstr "雅加达 REST 端点"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Servlet endpoint"
msgstr "Servlet 端点"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Reactive Routes endpoint"
msgstr "Reactive Routes 端点"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Funqy HTTP endpoint"
msgstr "Funqy HTTP 端点"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Build and Deploy to Google Cloud"
msgstr "构建并部署到 Google Cloud"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus forces a packaging of type `uber-jar` for your function as Google Cloud Function deployment requires a single JAR."
msgstr "Quarkus 会强制将您的函数打包为 `uber-jar` 格式，因为 Google Cloud Function 的部署需要单个 JAR 文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Package your application using the standard `mvn clean package` command.\n"
"The result of the previous command is a single JAR file inside the `target/deployment` directory that contains the classes and the dependencies of the project."
msgstr "使用标准命令 ``mvn clean package` ` 对应用程序进行打包。上述命令执行后，会在 ` `target/deployment` ` 目录中生成一个 JAR 文件，其中包含该项目的类文件及其依赖项。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Then you will be able to use `gcloud` to deploy your function to Google Cloud."
msgstr "然后，您就可以使用 `gcloud` 将您的函数部署到 Google Cloud 上了。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "We will use the Java 21 runtime, but you can switch to the Java 17 runtime by using `--runtime=java17` instead of `--runtime=java21` on the deploy commands."
msgstr "我们将使用 Java 21 运行时，但您可以在部署命令中将 `--runtime=java21` 替换为 `--runtime=java17` ，从而切换到 Java 17 运行时。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The entry point must always be set to `io.quarkus.gcp.functions.http.QuarkusHttpFunction` as this is the class that integrates Cloud Functions with Quarkus."
msgstr "入口点必须始终设置为 `io.quarkus.gcp.functions.http.QuarkusHttpFunction，` 因为该类负责将 Cloud Functions 与 Quarkus 集成。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The first time you launch this command, you can have the following error message:"
msgstr "首次运行此命令时，可能会出现以下错误信息："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This means that Cloud Build is not activated yet. To overcome this error, open the URL shown in the error, follow the instructions and then wait a few minutes before retrying the command."
msgstr "这意味着 Cloud Build 尚未启用。要解决此错误，请打开错误信息中显示的 URL，按照说明操作，然后等待几分钟再重试该命令。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This command will give you as output a `url` that points to your function."
msgstr "该命令将输出一个指向您该函数的 `URL` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can then call your endpoints via:"
msgstr "然后，您可以通过以下方式调用您的端点："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Jakarta REST: `{url}/hello`"
msgstr "对于雅加达 REST： `{url}/hello`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For servlet: `{url}/servlet/hello`"
msgstr "对于 Servlet： `{url}/servlet/hello`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Reactive Routes: `{url}/vertx/hello`"
msgstr "对于 Reactive Routes： `{url}/vertx/hello`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Funqy: `{url}/funqy`"
msgstr "Funqy： `{url}/funqy`"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Testing locally"
msgstr "本地测试"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The easiest way to locally test your function is using the Cloud Function invoker JAR."
msgstr "在本地测试函数的最简单方法是使用 Cloud Function 调用器 JAR 文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can download it via Maven using the following command:"
msgstr "您可以通过 Maven 使用以下命令下载它："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Before using the invoker, you first need to build your function via `mvn package`."
msgstr "在使用调用器之前，您需要先通过 ` `mvn package` ` 命令构建您的函数。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Then you can use it to launch your function locally."
msgstr "然后，你就可以用它在本地运行该函数了。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `--classpath` parameter needs to be set to the previously packaged JAR that contains your function class and all Quarkus related classes."
msgstr "`--classpath` 参数需要设置为之前打包的 JAR 文件，该文件中包含您的函数类以及所有与 Quarkus 相关的类。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Your endpoints will be available on http://localhost:8080."
msgstr "您的端点将可在 http://localhost:8080 上访问。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "What's next?"
msgstr "接下来呢？"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/gcp-functions-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can use our xref:funqy-gcp-functions.adoc[Google Cloud Functions Funqy binding] to use Funqy,\n"
"a provider-agnostic function as a service framework, that allow to deploy HTTP function or Background function to Google Cloud."
msgstr "您可以使用我们的 xref:funqy-gcp-functions.adoc[Google Cloud Functions Funqy 绑定] 来使用 Funqy——这是一个与提供商无关的“函数即服务”（FaaS）框架，可将 HTTP 函数或后台函数部署到 Google Cloud 上。"
